# Group Genre
Represents actions against Genre object

## Genre [/genre/{id}]
Represents a genre

+ Parameters
    + id (string, `1`) ... The id of the Genre.

+ Model (application/json)

    ```js
        {
            "data": {
                "id": 3,
                "parentId": 0,
                "title": "Action",
                "type": "Genre"
            },
            "messages": [
                {
                    "success": "Data successfully retrieved"
                }
            ]
        }
    ```

